Odaily Planet Daily News According to Lookonchain monitoring, an address deposited about 12.88 million USDC to Hyperliquid and shorted SOL, BTC and ETH with 5x leverage:
Short 17,670 SOL (US$3.048 million), opening price US$169.9, liquidation price US$877.15;
Short 15.5 BTC (US$1.61 million), opening price US$103,039.5, liquidation price US$917,160;
Short 564.5 ETH (US$1.365 million), opening price US$2,320.58, liquidation price US$24,585.
The current three positions have a total floating loss of more than US$114,000.
